metadata.description:
Yucca II is a part of Fissure, a body of work created to explore nocturnal, micro-landscapes using wet plate collodion process.  

Yucca II was originally created as a 20x24in ambrotype, taken at night in Joshua Tree.  The original was unfortunately broken while the piece was being installed in a gallery.  

This NFT is 1/1, 3487px x 4208px
